      "span_text": "Nested PCR with specifi c primers for P. falciparum and P. malariae, followed by sequence analysis of the SSUrRNA gene, and nested PCR, followed by sequence analysis of the pLDH gene, were negative for P. falciparum, positive for P. malariae, and negative for P. knowlesi"
